            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "(I-I wonder if I should talk to her...? The person at the store looks worried, too.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Urrrrrrrrrrrr."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Umm...hello, Linca. Are you shopping?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Ayesha, good timing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "What do you think about this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Wow, that's a cute hairpin!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I knew it. So it is cute..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I wonder if I should buy it...<CR>But, no."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "If I buy something impulsively,<CR> Marion will get mad at me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I have already wasted money recently..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "(I wonder what she bought...<CR>But, I think it's best not to ask.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But it's rare to see you showing an interest in accessories."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I thought you might not really care about things like this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd3,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "No, this is not for myself.<CR>I thought...it might look<CR>good on Marion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "She always buys things for me, so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "So it's a present for Marion...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Linca, you should buy it! I'm sure this would look great on Marion!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x39,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "And I think Marion would be very happy to get it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It's not too expensive, so she shouldn't get mad at you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I-I see. Then maybe I should jump right in and buy it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "The price does have two less zeros than the last purchase I made, so this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Ayesha. Because of you,<CR>I have decided to buy this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I shall buy every one of this<CR>hairpin they have here and give<CR>them to Marion..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat!? I'm sure just having one of the same hairpins is enough!"
        }
